                        <h1>Your Gift to the Humanities</h1>

<p>Donors like you fuel every aspect of education and discovery at the University of Chicago. Please complete the form below to make a one-time or recurring gift, or prepare for the future with a <a href="http://campaign.uchicago.edu/join-the-campaign/gift-planning">planned gift</a>.</p>
                        <kintera:webFeature/>
                    </div>
                    <div class="grid-3 region region-content-bottom-right" id="region-content-bottom-right">
                        <div class="region-inner region-content-bottom-right-inner">
                            <section class="block odd" id="">
                                <div class="block-inner clearfix">
                                    <h2 class="block-title">Why Give?</h2>
                                    <div class="content clearfix">
                                       <p>Our Division&rsquo;s students and faculty are boldly developing new scholarly approaches in their respective fields and contributing to the global exchange of ideas. Your support allows us to build on past successes, as we continue to support the intellectual ambitions of our gifted scholars. There are many ways to give to the Humanities, including donations of cash, gifts of securities, employer&rsquo;s matching gifts program, or through a planned gift. Please contact us directly for more information.</p>

                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </section>
                            <section class="block odd" id="">
                                <div class="block-inner clearfix">
                                    <h2 class="block-title">Questions</h2>
                                    <div class="content clearfix">
                                       <p>If you have questions about how philanthropy supports the Humanities at the University of Chicago, or where to direct a specific gift, please contact:</p>

<p>Dana Treglia, AM&rsquo;14<br />
Development Associate<br />
<a href="mailto:dtreglia@uchicago.edu">dtreglia@uchicago.edu</a><br />
773.702.9290</p>

                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </section>
                            <section class="block odd" id="">
                                <div class="block-inner clearfix">
                                    <h2 class="block-title">Safe &amp; Secure</h2>
                                    <div class="content clearfix">
                                       <p>The security of your information is very important to us. We use Secure Socket Layer (SSL) technology to protect the security of your online gift information.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </section>

                        </div>
